  <entry>
    <title>Codeforces Round</title>
    <link href="/2022/06/29/Codeforces-Round-803-Div-2/"/>
    <url>/2022/06/29/Codeforces-Round-803-Div-2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Codeforces-Round-803-Div-2"><a href="#Codeforces-Round-803-Div-2" class="headerlink" title="Codeforces Round #803 (Div. 2)"></a>Codeforces Round #803 (Div. 2)</h1><p><a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/1698">Codeforces Round #803 (Div. 2)</a></p><h2 id="A-XOR-Mixup"><a href="#A-XOR-Mixup" class="headerlink" title="A. XOR Mixup"></a>A. XOR Mixup</h2><p>题目涉及到异或运算</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/tg4sKzxrjT7boUH.png" alt="image-20220629130920547"></p><p>异或运算的逆运算是它本身，也就是说两次异或同一个数最后结果不变，如：3 ^ 4 ^ 4 &#x3D; 3。并且k^k&#x3D;0</p><p>因为对于题目给出的数组[a1,a2,a3….,an]:</p><p>a1&#x3D;a2^a3^a4……^an</p><p>a1^a2^a3……^an&#x3D;0</p><p>ax^[a1,a2,a3,…..an]&#x3D;ax</p><p>ax&#x3D;a1^a2….^an(without ax)</p><p>可知该题数组中的任何一个数都符合题目要求。</p><h2 id="B-Rising-Sand"><a href="#B-Rising-Sand" class="headerlink" title="B. Rising Sand"></a>B. Rising Sand</h2><p>Solution:</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/KbtNAFvISoCdhgf.png" alt="image-20220629134108909"></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> MAX = <span class="hljs-number">200007</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> MOD = <span class="hljs-number">1000000007</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n, k;<br>cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; k;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> a[n];<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; a[i];<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (k &gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt; n - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i++) &#123;<br>        res += (a[i] &gt; a[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] + a[i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>]);<br>    &#125;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; res &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; (n - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    ios::<span class="hljs-built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">false</span>);<br>    cin.<span class="hljs-built_in">tie</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> tt; cin &gt;&gt; tt; <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= tt; i++) &#123;<span class="hljs-built_in">solve</span>();&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// solve();</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>算法</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>常用git指令</title>
    <link href="/2022/06/28/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8git%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <url>/2022/06/28/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8git%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="常用git指令"><a href="#常用git指令" class="headerlink" title="常用git指令"></a>常用git指令</h1><h2 id="指令列表"><a href="#指令列表" class="headerlink" title="指令列表"></a>指令列表</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git init    --初始化仓库<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git add 文件名     --将文件添加到缓存区<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;添加信息标注&quot;</span> --将缓存区的文件添加到本地仓库<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git status    --查看仓库当前的状态<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git diff--缓存区和工作区文件的差异<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git <span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span>    --删除本地仓库的文件<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span>     --查看历史提交记录<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;github上注册的电子邮箱&quot;</span>              生成SSH<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git pull      --下载远程代码并合并<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git push      --上传文件至远程库<br>git push origin master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git remote add origin &lt;server&gt;--添加远程服务器<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">//http<br>git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7890--设置git全局代理<br>//https<br>git config --global https.proxy https://127.0.0.1:7890--设置git全局代理<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="相关资料"><a href="#相关资料" class="headerlink" title="相关资料"></a>相关资料</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/geeeeeeeeek/git-recipes">高质量的 Git 中文教程，源于国外社区的优秀文章和个人实践</a></p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/book/zh/v2">《Pro Git》Git官方书籍(中文)</a></p><h2 id="常见错误"><a href="#常见错误" class="headerlink" title="常见错误"></a>常见错误</h2><p>OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was aborted, errno 10054</p><p>解决方法参考:  <a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/fairylyl/p/15059437.html">作者：云梦&amp;&amp;玄龙</a>   或   <a href="https://blog.51cto.com/u_15326986/3328947">作者：Herio</a></p><h2 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h2><p>有时需将网络上查询到的部分指令中的  <em>master</em>  改为  <em>main</em> </p>]]></content>
    
    
    
